column4: NSLOCTEXT("[E5CFF2804D03F6891BCB4FB82EE7416D]", "308F9056483A4DD3DCBD50842DADBB0E", "Oh that? That\'s a <Important>Save Machine for Memory Card Battle Data</>.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E5CFF2804D03F6891BCB4FB82EE7416D]", "4E3CE74D4490B7B4CE5E5FA69D7809E7", "Using that machine, you can save your current partner\'s data for battle.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E5CFF2804D03F6891BCB4FB82EE7416D]", "69887A4442CFAA2E2301CFA97978B44C", "Just press Interact, and the machine will tell you what to do.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E5CFF2804D03F6891BCB4FB82EE7416D]", "4F8EF2BB48CD1A870567E7B635B76214", "Do you want to use the <Important>Save Machine for Memory Card Battle Data</>?")
